~ start
Sign: Hi! I'm everybody's favorite sign. And I'll teach you how this game works.
Sign: First you can walk around with WASD, but you probably already knew that.
Sign: Second you can spot white circles in the water, those are fishing spots!
Sign: When you see a fishing spot, throw your bobber at it with Left Mouse Button
Sign: You can stop fishing by pressing it again.
Sign: Wait long enough until a red ! appears above your head. You should press Right Mouse Button to reel it in.
Sign: You should take my word for it! I'm a sign it's my job!
=> END